 counted. Together with the\n358 particles published earlier, information about 2883 particles detected by\nthe dust instrument during Galileo's six years' journey to Jupiter is now\navailable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Sep 1998 16:53:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
